      </li>
      
      <li class="ctsh clearfix" data-cid="33697588">
        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/55812349/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u55812349-26.jpg" alt="金声" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/33697588/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/33697588/" class="">第39页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/55812349/" class=" " title="金声">金声</a>
              
                <span class="allstar30" title="还行"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="33697588">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">儒教要脱胎换骨，它必须有一个“去政治化”的程序。不然，它就常常会成为一个统治者利用的工具，就会被“污名化”。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2014-12-14 22:57</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                儒教要脱胎换骨，它必须有一个“去政治化”的程序。不然，它就常常会成为一个统治者利用的工具，就会被“污名化”。
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
